    {
      "id": "82f0f3af_4e2af5dd",
      "file_path": "cps-ncmp-service/src/main/java/org/onap/cps/ncmp/api/inventory/sync/ModuleSyncWatchdog.java",
      "patchset_number": 5,
      "line": 61,
      "message": "Yes, By adding these info logs to calculate timings for eatch operations. like below :\n\n1: Average time elapsed to get/ fetch cm handles by state ADVISED is (Total time elapsed in ms / total number of cm handles): Batch 1: (19404/601) = 32.28618968386023 and Batch 2: (3485/857) = 4.066511085180863\n32.28618968386023 +4.066511085180863 = 36.35270076904109/2 = 18.17635038452055 / iteration\n\n2: Average time elapsed to shuffle cm handle list of size : 601 is 0 ms and 857 is 0 ms = ~ 0 ms / iteration\n\n3: Average time elapsed to get yang model cm handles is: 63107/601= 105.0033277870216 and 37337/857 = 43.56709451575263 \n105.0033277870216 +43.56709451575263 =148.5704223027742/2= 74.28521115138711 ms / iteration \n\n4: Average time elapsed to get cm handle state with id is: First Batch (first iteration: 83 + second iteration: 7) = 90 + Second Batch (first iteration: 10 + second iteration: 12) = 22 \n\t(90+22)/ 2 = 56 ms /cm handle\n\n5: Average time elapsed to delete schema set If exists with id is: First Batch (first iteration: 17 + second iteration: 2) = 19 + Second Batch (first iteration: 2 + second iteration: 2) = 4 \n(19+4)/ 2 = 11.5 ms /cm handle\n\n6: Average Time elapsed to sync., create schema set and anchor with id is: First Batch (first iteration: 38393 + second iteration: 599) = 38992 + Second Batch (first iteration: 237 + second iteration: 122) = 359\n(38992 +359)/ 2 = 19675.5 ms /cm handle\n\n7: Average Time elapsed to save cm handle state with id is: First Batch (first iteration: 293 + second iteration: 84) = 377 + Second Batch (first iteration: 14 + second iteration: 8) = 22\n\t(84 + 22) / 2 = 53 ms /cm handle",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 7957,
        "name": "Sourabh Sourabh",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "sourabh.sharma.lnf@gmail.com",
        "username": "sourabh_sourabh"
      },
